{"tid":1359201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<那有警黑合作？> 元朗連日大反黑　搜查娛樂場所    拘捕11名721恐襲涉案人士","createTime":"2019-07-24T05:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:53:59.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"999172e71e8c8da7f93df108ab0f3a6b9d6ce315","tid":1359201,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:37:39.000Z","msg":"元朗連日大反黑　搜查娛樂場所 <br />\n<br />\n警方針對本周日(21日)西鐵元朗站「白衫軍」無差別追打市民事件，為打擊黑幫氣燄，警員一連兩日在區內夜場查牌。昨日(23日)晚上11時，警方再次出動近半百警力，掩至炮仗坊一帶多間娛樂場所查牌，並截查多名可疑男子包括南亞漢，暫時無人被捕，行動至今晨1時仍未結束。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日(23日)再於元朗、屯門及機場拘捕5名男子(39至51歲)，至今共拘捕11名涉案男子，部分人士具黑幫背景。<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/article/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91%E3%80%80%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%89%80-G1JM77\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Farticle%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2589%2580-G1JM77&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTewbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=f7f519bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/article/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%80%A3%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%8D%E9%BB%91%E3%80%80%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%89%80-G1JM77</a><br />\n<br />\n知道無啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6b2e30e480191ff26b5409236236c0561f38e9","tid":1359201,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"7.27 保護元朗居民     反對警黑合作"},{"pid":"625365bb293728bc407889c19d6508d780ae49cb","tid":1359201,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"放返晒啦<img src=\"/assets/